txt.en: Collect gifts of Rhûn within The Towers of the Teeth.

While exploring The Towers of the Teeth, you notice some treasures from the lands of Rhûn.

You take it upon yourself to collect these gifts of Rhûn for the Host of the West.

<rgb=#FF0000>Warning: This quest requires Towers of the Teeth: Guardian of the Depths to be underway. If that quest has been completed or failed, you will be unable to exit and re-enter this instance in order to complete this quest.</rgb>
Bring the gifts of Rhûn to Thurindol
Collect gifts of Rhûn within The Towers of the Teeth.
You should collect gifts of Rhûn and bring them to Thurindol.

While exploring The Towers of the Teeth, you notice some treasures from the lands of Rhûn.

You take it upon yourself to collect samples of these gifts of Rhûn treasures for the Host of the West.

<rgb=#FF0000>Warning: This quest requires Towers of the Teeth: Guardian of the Depths to be underway. If that quest has been completed or failed, you will be unable to exit and re-enter this instance in order to complete this quest.</rgb>>
'Indeed these are fine spoils of war. Someday, we may be glad to have them. We must keep focus on the task at hand for now, though.'
Bring the gifts of Rhûn to Thurindol
Towers of the Teeth: A Brush with Death
